		<title>Bitcoin SegWit Impact&#058; How Segregated Witness Improves Scalability</title>
		<link>https://securenest.org/learn/bitcoin-segwit-impact</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Alex Sterling]]></dc:creator>
